Class Menuitem

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.AbstractModel
      • models.menu.Menuitem

  • @Entity
public class Menuitem
extends AbstractModel
    Data model representing a Menuitem. MenuItems have a hierarchical structure. A Menuitem has one parent and can have multiple children.
